Interface ICorfuSMRProxy<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of the SMR object. Created by mwei on 11/10/16.
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ICorfuSMRProxyInternal<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CorfuCompileProxy

    public interface ICorfuSMRProxy<T>
    An interface for accessing a proxy, which manages an SMR object.
